S0.description:
#studywithme  #스윗미 #공부
 
[더보기란]
📢 Time table
* Every day : 08:00~24:00(Live), 24:00~08:00(Recorded)
* 상태표시 : 상단 현재시각 옆에 빨간불 들어오면 Live, 없으면 녹화방송(식사 및 기타)
* 12시~13시(점심식사), 18시~19시(저녁식사)
* 정기휴무 : 토요일
* 새벽방송은 녹방
* 창문속 화면은 서울의 실시간 중계입니다.

📢 시험 및 기간
* 23년 2월부터 감정평가사 준비중 
* [박문각 감정평가사]에서 지원을 받아 온라인으로 학습하고 있습니다.
* 종종 화면에 노출되는 강의 저작권에 관한 사항은 [박문각 감정평가사]로부터 사전 동의를 받았습니다.

📢 사용가능한 명령어
✔️  출첵 명령어 :  출첵,  ㅊㅊ, 복귀, ㅂㄱ
✔️  퇴첵 명령어 : 퇴첵,  ㅌㅊ, 외출, ㅇㅊ
✔️ 입장 명령어 : 중간고사방, 기말고사방, 모의고사방, 입시방, 공시방, 고시방, 학교방, 샤워방,
                               공부방, 인강방, 학원방, 과제방, 독서방, 운동방, 휴식방, 식사방, 간식방, 꿀잠방
✔️ 명언 명령어 : 명언-1에서부터 명언-41까지 예)명언-7
✔️ 명령어는 한 타임에 최대 3개정도만 해주세요. (도배는 타인에게 방해될수 있어요)

📢 information for foreigners
✔️ Hi, I am ziho in Korea. let’s study hard together!
✔️ I prepare for the exam once a year. If I pass the exam, I will be qualified to evaluate
      all real estate value in Korea.
✔️ Please chat during breaks, excluding commands and greetings.
✔️ commands : in, out, meal, study, break, back

📢 Product
✔️ 지워지는 볼펜 : 프릭션(4색 멀티 0.38mm, 노크존 0.7mm, 노크존 우드 0.7mm)
✔️ 지워지는 형광펜 : 프릭션(라이트, 라이트 네츄럴) 
✔️ 샤프 : 펜텔 그래프1000(+ain샤프심)
✔️ 컴퓨터 : LG 올인원
✔️ 스피커 : 미디플러스 MI3 II 3인치
✔️ 키보드, 마우스 : 로지텍 K380s, M350s
✔️ 계산기 : fx-9860g3
✔️ 독서대 : 셀프제작(가로 80cm)
✔️ 책상 : e-smart
✔️ 의자 : 시디즈 T50

📢 '열품타'를 운영하고 있습니다. 주20시간/주40시간
       - '공부하는지호'로 검색
       - 자세한건 커뮤니티 [열품타 공지]글을 참고해주세요.

📢 기타 내용
✔️ 출첵, 퇴첵 확인이 필요하신 분은 ‘좌측 상단의 시청기록-실시간 채팅’란에서 가능.
✔️ 채팅창 열어놓고 하시는분은, 불편한 채팅이 올라올시 '개인차단'기능을 이용하세요.

✔️ 나이, 성별 비공개
✔️ 악의적으로 반말, 비속어, 비아냥 거리시는 분은 바로 숨김처리합니다.
✔️ 과도한 친목으로 번질수 있는 인스타, 줌 등의 공유는 금지합니다. 

✔️ 디데이 적용을 원하시는분은 하루 전 업로드된 라이브에상에 댓글로 시험일/회차를 남겨주세요.
✔️ 노트북 배경화면은 강의 저작권 보호를 위해 사진으로써 연출한 것입니다.
✔️ 학습시간 시작과 끝에는 학교종이 울려요.
✔️ 채팅은 쉬는시간에 봐요.
✔️ 지호의 아침 지각벌금 : 누적 8000원

📢 문의
✔️ 인스타그램 : study.ziho
✔️ 메일 : study.ziho@gmail.com
✔️ 데스크테리어 제품 환영

📢 제작에 도움주신분들
✔️ 노래 - [아판뮤직] "바램" ARTIST : 박지윤, 이진헌 :  https://youtu.be/e0njles7ggI
✔️ GiGAeyesLiveTV : https://www.youtube.com/@GiGAeyesLiveTV(협의완료)
✔️ 지니어스 웹개발자 Mr.화해
✔️ 나눔뮤직 - https://tv.naver.com/v/13595048
✔️ ASMR은 무료파일을 직접 편집하였습니다.
✔️© a href='https://kr.123rf.com/profile_virtosmedia' virtosmedia/a,
 a href='https://www.123rf.com/free-images/'123RF Free Images/a
✔️ 제작된 채팅중 일부 이모티콘은 '김맛'님, 퍼블릭 도매인을 이용한 '정비서'님의 그림임.

S1.description:
"Greetings everyone, it's a pleasure to introduce myself. My name is Endrit and I'm currently pursuing my dream of becoming a doctor as a VI year medical student in the beautiful country of Italy. 

I believe that having great company and a support system can make all the difference in our lives, especially when it comes to our studies. That's why I hope to connect with all of you and form new friendships that not only make our studies more enjoyable but also help us grow and succeed together.

Let's make the most out of this journey and make our studies exciting and fulfilling! I'm looking forward to getting to know each and every one of you."


I stream everyday/almost everyday 12+ hours Pomodoro Sessions 60/10 with some exceptions. 

Stream is gonna start everyday or almost between 11:00 and 11:30 a.m. UTC +.1 If someday I won't be able to stream, i'll let you know in advance usually with a YT post. 


When life throws me a curveball and I can't stream on a scheduled day, I make sure to drop a heads up on my YT channel so y'all are in the know.

S2.description:
It is time to concentrate with the soothing sounds of white noise! Tune in to our first ever live stream as we play this relaxing sound all day long. Listen along with fellow studiers and prepare for a productive work session. This white noise sound helps you concentrate while studying or doing homework as the consistent sound helps block out background distractions and creates a soothing environment. Let it focus your mind and ease busy thoughts. Good luck on your exams! 

The Great American Total Solar Eclipse going over North America seemed like the talk of the town not too long ago! This white noise live stream features our recreation of a total solar eclipse as seen from space! 
Note: This is NOT a live stream of the Great American Eclipse.
We love solar eclipses and space scenes in general, so an eclipse white noise just seemed natural to us! We really hope you enjoy our interpretation! Goodnight! 

We all need to focus at times, especially if you're facing homework or drafting up a presentation for work. We may often find ourselves surrounded by distractions that can break our concentration such as loud coworkers or roommates. It's time to block all that out and focus better with the sound of white noise. Whether you need to concentrate on studying, reading, writing or exam prep, playing white noise in the background can really help. Be more productive with white noise for studying and focus!

S13.description:
⬇️⬇️ Links, schedule, and more information down below! ⬇️⬇️

Welcome! Come join for some motivation and accountability! Here we follow the 50/10 Pomodoro method, where we work for 50 minutes and then take a 10 minute break to chat, relax, craft and play puzzles! (we're obsessed with jumble words...)

I am a physics PhD student in my second year at the University of Auckland. My PhD is purely theoretical and computational, so I do lots of coding. My research looks at gravitational wave physics in relation to supermassive black holes and the future Laser Interferometer Space Antenna.

I did my undergraduate and masters in the UK, where I grew up, and then moved to New Zealand for my PhD. I now do purely research and don't take any classes, but I do teach some!

🌟 🌟Hola and welcome to live study session! 
Let’s enjoy this time together and get things done ^^.
Feel free to take a break any time and come back when you want.
The goal is to be productive but without exhausting yourself. 
A small break when you feel like it, it is always welcome.
Happy studying and working! 📚💼🎧

Some tips to have a good study or reading session
~ Always keep a water bottle with you
~ Always have a charger with you 
~ Put headphones on (if you have them)
~ Put music on if you like it
~ During breaks move, get fresh air
~ Keep your phones off
~ Avoid any distractions
~ Do one thing at the time
Where are you joining and what are you studying?
Let me know in the chat session.

S18.description:
📚 Study With Me – Architecture & Focus 🎧

Welcome to my Study With Me sessions! 🎓 I’m an architecture student sharing my live study sessions to help you stay motivated and focused. Whether you’re studying architecture, design, or any other subject, join me for a productive and calm study atmosphere.

🔹 Live Session Format:
✅ Pomodoro technique (50 min focus / 10 min break)
✅ Lo-Fi music & study vibes
✅ Motivation & consistency

💬 Share your study goals in the chat, and let’s stay on track together! Don’t forget to subscribe so you don’t miss a session.

📍 Every day, there will be a live stream. Feel free to keep up with my pace—or challenge yourself to study even more! The key is to find your own rhythm. Study when you feel the most focused or creative. But if you'd like to sync with my schedule, join the live session, chat with me and others during breaks, and stay motivated together.

Most importantly, don’t forget to take breaks and look after your health. I truly wish you the best on your journey to becoming the person you aspire to be. 💪✨
